{"tid":251750,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：黃毓民無貨賣，是低智力辯論者。","createTime":"2017-05-21T07:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T17:21:49.000Z","uid":319,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2254798ad7d92a298c7f47bdf544911917277f","tid":251750,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:54:54.000Z","msg":"Wan Chin<br />\n<br />\n4 hrs &middot; <br />\n<br />\n陳雲：青山（精神病院）是低智力辯論者的最後論據。正所謂，辯到絕境說痴線，詞窮理屈出青山。<br />\n網友Z. I.: //黃毓民講得出入青山，佢真係駁唔到國師，好多人包括長毛都同國師so called辯論過，結論都係陳雲入青山，而黃毓民講得出呢句，證明佢已經無貨賣。//<br />\n<br />\nWan Chin 講還講，唔好講青山。否則你一鋪清袋。出來論政幾十年，最後竟然出青山，毓民老哥，還是補選立法會，取回議席罵港共啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155235209137225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155235209137225&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a2578150\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155235209137225</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：講還講，唔好講我屋企！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3c905fc70fe3d88ceafaa08e39ffe4d3d48ab6","tid":251750,"uid":33605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"吓，佢真係一啲自知之明都冇囉<br />\n成日以為自己好勁，日日打飛機，吹到侵侵睇佢Facebook，其實咁樣一啲都唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4304c95285fe5cf4193ab17cee92a171eff6b695","tid":251750,"uid":33605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"係，蟈屍係有學識嘅，但係點解成日喺facebook打埋啲迷之發言？仲要冇啦啦加句「智力閲讀門檻：xxx」？大佬啊，你咁樣係侮辱緊選民，話佢哋蠢啊！"},{"pid":"6a3553ea0f76d48cfde5523c61122a612752f030","tid":251750,"uid":33605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"DLLM忍咗佢好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收手啦好冇？<br />\n放過本土派好冇？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0eb38dc73aa340d060d643f9d8c956